OL,5, Former senior civil servant Sue Gray   
OL,6, has been cleared to start working for  
OL,7, the Labour Party from September.       
OL,9,FParliament's appointments advisory body
OL,10,Frecommended a six month break from when
OL,11,Fshe quit as an official in March.      
OL,13,FSome Tories had expressed anger that   
OL,14,Fshe was offered a job as Labour leader 
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer's chief of staff.     
OL,17,FThey said it undermined the            
OL,18,Fimpartiality of her report on lockdown 
OL,19,Fgatherings in No 10, which contributed 
OL,20,Fto Boris Johnson's downfall.           
